Appendix I (An Integral Part of this License) Restricted Anime List

This Appendix forms an integral part of this License and shall have the same force and effect as the body of this License. Unless the context otherwise requires, the anime titles listed in this Appendix shall collectively be referred to as the "anime on the Restricted List."

The anime titles below shall be filled in, replaced, or supplemented by the copyright holder as needed; once filled in, replaced, or supplemented, they shall fall within the scope of the "Restricted List" referred to in Sections 2 and 3 of this License.

